data.description: Welcome home! Stunning 4 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath home nestled in a very quiet cove! Previous owner's made over $80,000 in updates! This beauty comes with a very spacious, open kitchen w/island, huge great room w/ sunroom off the great room, hardwood and tile throughout, & new roof in 2018. The 4th bedroom has it's own private stairway & bathroom! The subdivision has community lakes, pool, pool house, play ground & tennis courts! Hurry and schedule your private showing before it's gone!
